			<CASNumber>3775</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Isopropamide ( R79) is a long-acting anticholinergic drug. It is used in the treatment of peptic ulcers and other gastrointestinal disorders involving hyperacidity (gastrointestinal acidosis) and hypermotility. It contains a quaternary ammonium group and is most often provided as an iodide salt. It is also used for the treatment of other gastrointestinal disorders like nervous dyspepsia and irritable bowel.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">异丙酰胺（R79）是一种长效抗胆碱能药物。它可用于治疗消化性溃疡和其他涉及胃酸过多（胃肠道酸中毒）和胃肠蠕动亢进的胃肠道疾病。它含有季铵基团，通常以碘盐的形式提供。它还可用于治疗神经性消化不良和肠易激等其他胃肠道疾病。</common:generalComment>
